import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import App from "./components/App"
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"

import { ChakraProvider } from "@chakra-ui/react"

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <ChakraProvider>
    <App />
    </ChakraProvider>
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
);
